&lt;li&gt;Partner with mechanical and manufacturing engineers to integrate high-power converter modules and stacks with thermal management systems, racking, structural support, and system-level cabinet into manufacturable designs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design layouts to minimize the critical effects of circuit parasitics - e.g. loop inductance, and gate loop parasitics, to manage voltage overshoot, ringing, and electromagnetic interference (EMI).&lt;/li&gt;
